Package net.minestom.server.utils

Class RGBColor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minestom.server.utils.RGBColor
  • public final class RGBColor
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a color in a text. You can either use one of the pre-made colors or make your own using RGB. fromRGB(byte, byte, byte).

    Immutable class.
